      <title>苹果取代高盛的理想信用卡合作伙伴是大通银行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2023-12-03/apple-to-drop-goldman-sachs-for-apple-card-chase-bank-is-ideal-replacement-lppjbe7z</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苹果和高盛正处于分拆的边缘，大通银行是介入的理想合作伙伴。此外：Sonos 已准备好在耳机和电视机顶盒领域与苹果和其他公司展开竞争；苹果继续关注6G；新的零售店即将到来。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2023-12-03/apple-to-drop-goldman-sachs-for-apple-card-chase-bank-is-ideal-replacement-lppjbe7z</guid>
